Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:52.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:58.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling like to you it was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.41,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:09.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:15.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:27.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the time we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:32.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}that the world was in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}We were wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:43.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}maybe it wasn't 'cause \Nyou're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:49.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}At every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:54.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:22:00.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can believe, I can believe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:05.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:12.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:52.35,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你伸出柔弱的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:58.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你笑得如此自然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.41,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}也許虛無縹緲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:09.18,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}但這是我力所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:15.25,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你漫不經心地觸碰我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:19.04,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}對我卻是無上榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:27.36,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}我們所信仰的每分每秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:32.84,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}世界就掌握在我們手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.74,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}陰差陽錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:43.81,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}也許此刻我們緊扣的雙手並無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:49.43,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}每分每秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:54.97,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}無所不在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:22:00.30,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}我深信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:05.48,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}當我握住你溫暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:12.85,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你溫暖的手
